
weatherman requires curl and bash version 3 or greater.

To install it, simply copy weatherman to your desired location and make it executable:

    $ cp weatherman /usr/bin
    $ chmod a+x /usr/bin/weatherman

To date, weatherman has only been tested on GNU/Linux and may not work on all platforms.

Please send bug reports to <subrosa at darkhorse dot nu>.  Thank you.

